            "heading": "What is Huk Gear?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Huk Gear is <em>the<\/em> technical performance fishing company dedicated to making life on the water more enjoyable from the first cast to the last. We are your destination for best-in-class performance fishing gear. We offer a wide range of apparel and accessories for men, women and kids designed to enhance comfort, protection and performance for anglers and outdoor enthusiasts.<\/p>",
